OL,5, A pub has almost halved its selection  
OL,6, of draught beer and cider for the      
OL,7, winter due to soaring energy bills.    
OL,9,FMichelle Knight, who runs the Six Bells
OL,10,Fin Coity, Bridgend, said reducing the  
OL,11,Fnumber of barrels would make her       
OL,12,Fcooling system more efficient.         
OL,14,FShe has pinned her energy bills up to  
OL,15,Fshow punters why she is having to make 
OL,16,Ftough choices to keep their local open.
OL,18,FThe UK government said the energy bills
OL,19,Frelief scheme was protecting           
OL,20,Fbusinesses.                            
